text: ""Some o" them do, aye," said Rob Anybody as the log began to speed up. #Wintersmith

passages.full_quote: "<used>Some o" them do</used>n't even ken where they are, poor souls
""A l<used>ot o" them do, aye," said</used> Billy
""Ach, they dinna like the taste o" us overmu<used>ch," said Rob Anybody as the</used> shadows parted
